                         T defaultValue,
                         Collection<T> possibleValues)
        Constructor. Note the T must implement toString().
        Parameters:
        name - the name of this property, for display in the UI.
        defaultValue - the default value, if any. May not be null.
        possibleValues - a Collection of possible values. If set to null no validation will be performed, if set to an empty list then values are presumed to be set at runtime.
